[global.policy]

  --- error hierarchy ---

  errors:
    SystemError
      DatabaseError       transient, retriable
      NetworkError        transient, retriable
      TimeoutError        transient, retriable
      ServiceUnavailable  transient, retriable

    ClientError
      ValidationError
      AuthorizationError
      NotFoundError
      ConflictError

    BusinessError
      PolicyViolation
      LimitExceeded
      StateError
      CircularDependencyError

  --- policies ---

  RetryPolicy:
    maximum attempts: 3
    backoff: exponential
    initial delay: 1 second

  PaginationPolicy:
    default page size: 50
    maximum page size: 200

  ItemPolicy:
    maximum title length: 300 characters
    maximum body length: 50000 characters
    maximum tags per item: 20

  TagPolicy:
    maximum tag name length: 100 characters
    tag names: lowercase, trimmed, no leading/trailing whitespace

  DependencyPolicy:
    maximum dependencies per item: 50
    circular dependencies: always rejected
    dependency graph maximum depth: 20 levels

  ImportPolicy:
    maximum file size: 10 MB
    supported formats: markdown (.md)
    maximum items per import batch: 500

  ArchivePolicy:
    archived items are never deleted
    archived items are excluded from default views
    archived items remain searchable
    archived items retain all relationships
